fields.Title: FRITTE / APOTHECARY
fields.Description: A small cabinet on the wall, right next to the posters.

fields.Title: You: ""A bottle of magnesium, please.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "A bottle of magnesium, please."

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""Uhm... I don't know, let's see......"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Uhm... I don't know, let's see... Nosaphed is a nasal spray. Drouamine is a really good painkiller. Magnesium is a dietary supplement. Hypnogamma is..." She stops.

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""Uhm..." She chews her bubblegum ab..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Uhm..." She chews her bubblegum absent-mindedly. "No, sorry. I'm not, like, a doctor or anything."

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "She is right! Saint-Batiste the com..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She is right! Saint-Batiste the company derives its name from Saint-Batiste the city, itself so named... because that's what it is. A rare case where that really is the full etymological history -- as far as almost anyone knows, at least.

fields.Title: You: ""Can I have Nosaphed?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Can I have Nosaphed?"

fields.Title: You: ""Who is Saint-Batiste?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who is Saint-Batiste?"

fields.Title: You: ""I want to buy some ammonia.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I want to buy some ammonia."

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["gates.fritte_asked_ammonia"] == true  and  ((Variable["TASK.get_ammonium_done"] == false  and  Variable["TASK.inspect_body_parts"] == false)  or  IsTaskActive("TASK.contact_warship_archer"))

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""Mkay, here. I hope Saint-Batiste m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mkay, here. I hope Saint-Batiste makes you feel better or something."

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""I don't really know what Hypnogamm..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't really know what Hypnogamma is. I guess it makes you feel less shit? It's recommended to use after lots of partying, studying, or exercising."

fields.Title: You: ""Do you have any ammonia?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you have any ammonia?"

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: (Variable["TASK.get_ammonium"] == true  and  Variable["gates.fritte_asked_ammonia"] == false  and  Variable["TASK.inspect_the_dead_body_done"] == false  and  Variable["TASK.inspect_body_parts"] == false  and  Variable["gates.fritte_got_ammonia"] == false)  or  (IsTaskActive("TASK.contact_warship_archer")  and  Variable["church.soona_mentioned_ammonia"] == true  and  Variable["gates.fritte_asked_ammonia"] == false)

fields.Title: You: ""I'll take some Hypnogamma.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'll take some Hypnogamma."

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""M'kay." She hands you a small caps..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "M'kay." She hands you a small capsule. "Don't, like... over-do it or something."

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""Mkay, here. I hope Saint-Batiste m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mkay, here. I hope Saint-Batiste makes you feel better or something."

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""Uhm, just ask me if you need anyth..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Uhm, just ask me if you need anything from Saint-Batiste. We don't stock prescription meds, but we do have nosaphed, drouamine, magnesium and hypnogamma."

fields.Title: You: ""What do those products do?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do those products do?"

fields.Title: Tutorial Agent: "NOSAPHED heals +1 Health. DROUAMINE..."
fields.Dialogue Text: NOSAPHED heals +1 Health. DROUAMINE heals +3 Health. MAGNESIUM heals +1 Morale. HYPNOGAMMA heals +3 Morale.

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: "Her nose is already back in her mag..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her nose is already back in her magazine. "Uh-huh."

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "Their logo is the bloodless rose --..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Their logo is the bloodless rose -- pure white, untouched by harm.

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""Mkay, here. I hope Saint-Batiste m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mkay, here. I hope Saint-Batiste makes you feel better or something."

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""Mkay, here. I hope Saint-Batiste m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mkay, here. I hope Saint-Batiste makes you feel better or something."

fields.Title: Saint-Batiste Pharmaceutics: "A small cabinet on the wall is fill..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A small cabinet on the wall is filled with various medicine bottles, nasal sprays and blister packs. They all bear the Saint-Batiste Pharmaceutics logo.

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""Saint-Batiste? You know..." She no..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Saint-Batiste? You know..." She nods slowly at the cabinet. "The pharmaceuticals company?"

fields.Title: You: ""Can you be a little more... specif..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Can you be a little more... specific?"

fields.Title: You: ""Thank you for explaining, miss.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thank you for explaining, miss."

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""Saint-Batiste Pharmaceuticals? The..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Saint-Batiste Pharmaceuticals? The one that sells meds out of Saint-Batiste?" She points to the cabinet. "That one? There?"

fields.Title: Frittte clerk: ""Yeah... there's like an ampoule so..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah... there's like an ampoule somewhere." She waves her hand in the air absent-mindedly.

fields.Title: Saint-Batiste Pharmaceutics: "A small cabinet on the wall is fill..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A small cabinet on the wall is filled with various medicine bottles, nasal sprays and blister packs. They all bear the Saint-Batiste Pharmaceutics logo.

fields.Title: You: ""I need Drouamine.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I need Drouamine."
